.TH carch 1 "June 18, 2026" Carch Carch
.SH NAME
carch \- A CLI tool to automate Linux system setup
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcarch\fR [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] [\fB\-c\fR|\fB\-\-catppuccin\-mocha\fR] [\fB\-d\fR|\fB\-\-dracula\fR] [\fB\-g\fR|\fB\-\-gruvbox\fR] [\fB\-n\fR|\fB\-\-nord\fR] [\fB\-r\fR|\fB\-\-rose\-pine\fR] [\fB\-\-fav\fR] [\fB\-\-unfav\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIsubcommands\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
A Rust\-based CLI tool to streamline and automate your Linux system\*(Aqs initial setup.
It offers automated scripts that save users time setting up their Linux environment.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version information
.TP
\fB\-c\fR, \fB\-\-catppuccin\-mocha\fR
Set theme to Catppuccin Mocha
.TP
\fB\-d\fR, \fB\-\-dracula\fR
Set theme to Dracula
.TP
\fB\-g\fR, \fB\-\-gruvbox\fR
Set theme to Gruvbox
.TP
\fB\-n\fR, \fB\-\-nord\fR
Set theme to Nord
.TP
\fB\-r\fR, \fB\-\-rose\-pine\fR
Set theme to Rosé Pine
.TP
\fB\-\-fav\fR \fI<THEME>\fR
Save the given theme as favorite and exit
.TP
\fB\-\-unfav\fR
Clear the saved favorite theme
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
\fBcheck-update\fR
Check for updates
.TP
\fBupdate\fR
Update the application
.TP
\fBuninstall\fR
Uninstall the application
.TP
\fBcompletions\fR
Generate shell completions (bash, zsh, fish)
.TP
\fBhelp\fR
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
.SH DOCUMENTATION
Comprehensive documentation for Carch is available at:
